cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.AI, cs.DC, cs.SI 

This paper discusses challenges in the risk management of smart card based electronic cash industry, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the evaluation of distributed intelligence function using micro dynamic simulation, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The simulation of electronic cash economy and transaction environment involves distributed computing (cs.DC) and the detection capability of off-chip, host-based counterfeit detection systems involves system and information theory (cs.SI).
